{"tid":2271396,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"沒見過乳溝的女人 - 李純恩","createTime":"2020-11-04T13:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T13:56:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e40ea91ea914959710f7ab0df2b3a451d37f8505","tid":2271396,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T13:56:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201104/NSRM4WB6IBAXBAL66BKFPRU55E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201104%2FNSRM4WB6IBAXBAL66BKFPRU55E%2F&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2Fxqha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=77103e8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201104%2FNSRM4WB6IBAXBAL66BKFPRU55E%2F&h=4ad84ad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201104/NSRM4WB6IBAXBAL66BKFPRU55E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n沒見過乳溝的女人 - 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FhmSO_J1yEvedvzukSQr01YMrz4=/6576x4384/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3VDVFRZCX5HSNIRVOIUIUXMLJU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFhmSO_J1yEvedvzukSQr01YMrz4%3D%2F6576x4384%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3VDVFRZCX5HSNIRVOIUIUXMLJU.JPG&h=9df0cf15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有區議員聽一個女播音員說，看了西九龍中心外牆上一系列漫畫美女像說「嚇了一跳」，便也跳了起來，「為民請命」，展開投訴，恰逢颱風刮至，美女像被收起，區議員竊喜，剛想宣揚「成功爭取」的功績，不料颱風過後，商場外牆上美女再現，且接二連三，越發精采，更加痛快。<br />\n<br />\n有一種人，不管大事小事，總是喜歡說「嚇了一跳」，以示問題的嚴重性。好像不「嚇了一跳」，就不是大事，把他嚇了一跳，事情就大了。是什麼人隔三差五就被「嚇了一跳」呢？就是那種沒有見識的人，沒有見識的人，少見多怪，看見什麼都大驚小怪，都「嚇了一跳」。卻不知道，他「嚇了一跳」的事情其實稀鬆平常，全世界都相安無事，只有他被「嚇了一跳」，左也「嚇了一跳」，右也「嚇了一跳」，好像心靈脆弱如玻璃，卻又不見被嚇死。<br />\n<br />\n這種沒見識的人，又常常覺得自己比許多人有見識，覺得自己要站出來說話，然後自然有區議員這類生物見機行事，跳出來「為民請命」。這種人。。。。。。。。。。。。"}]}